# Cloudflare Pages routing.
#
# Root → photoreal scene demo (Juggernaut XL → 167k Gaussians). The flagship.
# /uvw  → procedural UVW bijection demo (explains the data structure).
# /atlas → same as /uvw.
# /docs → markdown-rendered README at /readme (the .html ext is auto-stripped
#         by Cloudflare so readme.html is reachable at /readme directly).
#
# Cloudflare auto-strips .html, so all targets use canonical extensionless URLs.
# Don't redirect /readme to /readme — that's a self-loop. Just rely on the
# auto-strip behaviour to serve readme.html at the /readme path.
/        /scene_demo  302
/uvw     /uvw_demo    302
/atlas   /uvw_demo    302
/docs    /readme      302
